  <brief_title>Comparison of the Frequency-altering AKE-1 Capsule and Pillcam SB2</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-center Randomized Head-to-head Comparison of the Frequency-altering AKE-1 Capsule and Pillcam SB2</official_title>
